column85: Cont1 Valve Or Device Fail Ind

column168: XPO Logistics terminal LHO experienced a release from a 5-gallon poly pail due to a puncture caused by improper dunnage. ERTS dispatched contractors to conduct cleanup operations. Contractors arrived onsite and confirmed approximately 3-gallons of product released to 3' x 4' area of the trailer floor & a 3' x 3' area of the asphalt lot below due to a puncture. Absorbents were deployed and worked into the impacted areas. The damaged pail & cleanup debris were then placed into a 55-gallon poly drum. The waste was staged onsite for terminal personnel to manage.
